def is_palindrome(s):
    s = ''.join((e for e in s if e.isalnum()))
    s = s.lower()
    start = 1
    end = len(s) - 1
    while start < end:
        if s[start] != s[end]:
            return False
        start += 1
        end -= 1
    return True
